:name:
Umbra I

:coretxt:
Ability to move shadows. 
Can be used to terrify or to aid hiding.
Can be used to create unnatural darkness.
Sunlight will always immediatly disperse shadows.
Strong light sources can also disperse these shadows.

:cost:
1 Instinct

:req:
Has feeded on some human that sun has never touched.

:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricMysticism
